data.description: Cute and cozy single-level home with attached garage and spectacular deck. This 2-bedroom 1.5-bath delivers year-round comfort with an efficient heating and cooling heat pump. The home’s large master bedroom is a true retreat, featuring vaulted ceilings, abundant built-in storage, and windows that frame the wildlife frequented hillside. A glass slider opens the dining room to an expansive back deck that offers both an impressive entertaining area as well as a tranquil space. In addition to the bedrooms, is a separate bonus room perfect for an office space.  Make this delightful home yours! Contact John Ague at 406-283-1138, or your real estate professional.
